proposalTitle: AI-Powered Edge Computing for Smart Cities
projectSummary: This project explores the integration of AI algorithms into edge devices to enhance data processing in smart city infrastructure.
objectives: 1. Develop lightweight AI models for edge deployment. 2. Reduce latency in urban IoT networks. 3. Improve data privacy at the edge.
expectedOutput: A working prototype of an edge AI device, published research paper, open-source toolkit."
